The evidence with the title ''inner cities' are a solution, not a problem - The Boston Globe ' says Oct 2, 2016  ... The current GOP presidential nominee talks about urban America in similarly apocalyptic terms . “ inner-city crime is reaching record levels, ” he's insisted, even though rates of violence in most cities have plunged over a generation . “ you walk down the street , you get shot, ” he said in monday's debate. 
